{"ts":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-k0nl2w"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Sentry PM-CLI-2E: directory-shaped settings.json crashes CLI bootstrap"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Harden settings bootstrap so a settings.json path that exists but is not a readable regular file yields deterministic settings diagnostics instead of propagating EISDIR before health, validation, or storage-integrity commands can run."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":1},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["area:config","area:storage","observability","resilience","sentry"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Directory-shaped or otherwise unreadable settings.json never crashes readSettingsWithMetadata; callers receive a deterministic warning and fallback settings; normal, missing, invalid-JSON, and invalid-schema behavior remains stable; CLI acceptance, full exact coverage, release gates, and the live Sentry gate pass."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-o2kc"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/severity","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/environment","value":"production"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/repro_steps","value":"Create .agents/pm/settings.json as a directory and run any pm command that bootstraps settings, such as pm health --check-only."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/expected_result","value":"CLI bootstrap remains available and surfaces a machine-readable settings warning that directs the operator to repair the unreadable settings path."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/actual_result","value":"readFileIfExists rethrows EISDIR from readSettingsWithMetadata, creating Sentry PM-CLI-2E before validation can report storage integrity."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/affected_version","value":"2026.7.21"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/fixed_version","value":"next"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/component","value":"core/store/settings"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/regression","value":true},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-f5hy2n","kind":"discovered_from","created_at":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z"},{"id":"pm-o1c53b","kind":"discovered_from","created_at":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z"},{"id":"pm-xdn6","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z"}]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-21T12:25:47.265Z","author":"codex-root","text":"text=Duplicate check: searched all pm statuses for PM-CLI-2E, readFileIfExists EISDIR settings, and settings.json directory. No canonical item covers this bootstrap failure. Fresh Sentry event 31835fc7f0cb4db789e12191560cf5b9 occurred once at 2026-07-21T11:37:08Z in readFileIfExists/readSettingsWithMetadata during malformed-settings acceptance."}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"b8ed72510461b71e66ae5e4c7999bbe7fca17e923c55742d304eec16d7a7d667","message":"Track PM-CLI-2E bootstrap resilience regression"}
